reddish with inner dark castaneous stripe; Laterotergites 
<number id="3DD724A56A58C11C1356FCFF41B2FC2B" box="[639,653,874,898]" pageId="2" pageNumber="65" value="9.0">9</number>
dark castaneous, subtriangular with apex rounded.
</paragraph>
